cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use AI-Testing-Loops in your work, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "AI-Testing-Loops"
abstract: >-
  A production-grade collection of 100 gold-standard testing loops for AI/LLM
  systems covering evaluation, guardrails, stress testing, QA, red-teaming, and
  reliability engineering. Each loop is a self-contained, reusable module with
  YAML configuration, automation scripts, and framework mappings to OWASP LLM
  Top 10, NIST AI RMF, and MITRE ATLAS.
authors:
  - name: "AI-Testing-Loops Contributors"
version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2025-01-01"
license: Apache-2.0
repository-code: "https://github.com/user/AI-Testing-Loops"
keywords:
  - ai-testing
  - llm-evaluation
  - guardrails
  - stress-testing
  - red-teaming
  - quality-assurance
  - production-reliability
  - owasp-llm
  - nist-ai-rmf
  - mitre-atlas
